comments.body: And this is only like the 5th documentation on iNat in DFW metroplex.  Very nice.  @brentano needs to find this one too.  ;)
I had combined it with an observation of 2 Clouded skippers.  @arbutterflynut caught it and let me know.
Wow!  This is a new one for ONP too!  :)
